Package: soccerstats
Title: Common Soccer Statistics and Example Data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Brian", "Waismeyer", 
                  email = "bwaismeyer@gmail.com", 
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package is a collection of functions that implement common
             statistics observed in analyses of soccer players, teams, and
             organizations. The package is explicitly designed to support
             learning about soccer data analysis and includes references to
             external sources, careful code documenation, and example data
             and vignettes.
URL: https://github.com/bwaismeyer/soccerstats
BugReports: https://github.com/bwaismeyer/soccerstats/issues
Depends: R (>= 3.2.2)
Imports: 
    dplyr,
    tidyr
License: GNU General Public License v3.0
LazyData: true
